ne&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;[&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;I&amp;#x27;m a relative reference to a repository file&lt;/span&gt;](&lt;span class=&#34;link&#34;&gt;../blob/master/LICENSE&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;[&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;You can use numbers for reference-style link definitions&lt;/span&gt;][&lt;span class=&#34;symbol&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Or leave it empty and use the [link text itself]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Some text to show that the reference links can follow later.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;[&lt;span class=&#34;symbol&#34;&gt;arbitrary case-insensitive reference text&lt;/span&gt;]: &lt;span class=&#34;link&#34;&gt;https://hexo.io&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;[&lt;span class=&#34;symbol&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;]: &lt;span class=&#34;link&#34;&gt;https://hexo.io/docs/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;[&lt;span class=&#34;symbol&#34;&gt;link text itself&lt;/span&gt;]: &lt;span class=&#34;link&#34;&gt;https://hexo.io/api/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbQ==&#34;&gt;I’m an inline-style link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbQ==&#34;&gt;I’m an inline-style link with title&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlv&#34;&gt;I’m a reference-style link&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
