&lt;p&gt;Or leave it empty and use the &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2FwaS8=&#34;&gt;link text itself&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
